snippet.title: CODE VEIN - DLC 1 - Hellfire Knight
snippet.description:
Through fire and flames, Hellfire Knight has his gaze locked on the Revenants. Prepare to challenge this powerful new enemy in DLC 1!

CODE VEIN is available now on PS4, XBOX ONE, & PC!
https://bandainam.co/CV2
